<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="shower-n">shower <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ʃaʊə(r)/    美 /'ʃaʊər/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>阵雨；淋浴 (器)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Tom was caught in a shower yesterday.
汤姆昨天淋了雨。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>take</strong> / <strong>have a hot shower</strong>
淋热水浴</p></div></div>